### =============== Authentication Endpoints ===============

### Register new user (No token returned)
POST {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "role": "Admin"
}

### Login (Returns token)
POST {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Refresh Token (replace with actual refresh token from login response)
POST {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Logout (replace userId with actual user id)
POST {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout/1

### =============== Test Protected Endpoints ===============

### Public endpoint (no auth required)
GET {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/test/public

### Protected endpoint (requires valid JWT)
GET {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/test/protected
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Admin endpoint (requires Admin role)
GET {{DemoGeoServer_HostAddress}}/api/test/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

